<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br><br>Thank you for purchasing with Kingsbridge!<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you have any questions at any time, please send me an email and I’ll be happy to help.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>We use&nbsp;<b>Feefo</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, an independent review service for our reviews and they may email you directly with a review request.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you were to rate the service I’ve provided and mention my name in this review it would be greatly appreciated.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
